{"tid":320285,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港視就發聲明 歡迎新一屆特區政府的決定","createTime":"2017-07-13T12:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T20:48:28.000Z","uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8292d5ccb6ad69830d0322d9fbf86b6319f5a2cb","tid":320285,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:12:17.000Z","msg":"港視就發聲明，歡迎新一屆特區政府的決定，希望日後能夠為香港市民提供更多電視娛樂節目的選擇。聲明指，港視2013年12月收購流動電視的相關牌照及頻譜；由於先前使用的制式只能支援VCD畫面質素的廣播，故申請以Digital Terrestrial Multimedia Broadcast制式（DTMB）廣播。唯因通訊局認為該制式可能引超過5,000指明處所接收到流動電視服務，有關的制式申請不獲批准。港視其後向有關當局申請以DVB-T2制式廣播而獲批。DVB-T2制式是歐洲普遍使用的先進制式，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">市民只需加裝指定接收器，便可在各式電視機上收看HD或4K高質素的節目。港視稍後會再作詳細公佈</span></span>。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"e867069c504e15693c45ec7a34808ad4eae9eb42","tid":320285,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:17:02.000Z","msg":"咩接收器？<br />\n天線？"},{"pid":"66776ffe5ad139a9bec5373980f5a28345b3ac49","tid":320285,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩接收器？<br />\n天線？</blockquote><br />\n天線連解碼裝置，可作家長鎖碼，特定播出用途 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32de5ee162d85c7764df63ac250ece382d26acee","tid":320285,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:22:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩接收器？<br />\n天線？</blockquote><br />\n天線連解碼裝置，可作家長鎖碼，特定播出用途 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大廈每家裝天線？"},{"pid":"2af85d759db07ff45596884eae6145203c2166af","tid":320285,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩接收器？<br />\n天線？</blockquote><br />\n天線連解碼裝置，可作家長鎖碼，特定播出用途 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大廈每家裝天線？</blockquote><br />\n簡單講，係「準流動收費電視」<img src=\"/asset